ed="T" n="0750c19"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0750c19"/><head><date from-iso="+0960-02-09" key="j20717322132856" to-iso="+1127-06-18"><anchor xml:id="beg0750007"/>宋<anchor xml:id="end0750007"/></date><placeName key="PL000000012759"><placeName>秀州</placeName><placeName>靈光寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A010003">皓端</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0750c20"/><persName key="A010003">釋皓端</persName>，姓<name>張</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000012751">嘉禾</placeName>人也。<date key="j20490492049413" from-iso="+0898-01-01" to-iso="+0898-12-31">九歲</date>，捨家入<placeName key="PL000000012759">靈<lb
ed="T" n="0750c21"/>光精舍</placeName>，師授經法，如溫舊業焉。年登<date key="j20530662053430" from-iso="+0909-01-01" to-iso="+0909-12-31">弱<lb
ed="T" n="0750c22"/>冠</date>，受形俱<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1189"/>無表<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1278"/>。于<placeName key="PL000000012309"><placeName>四明</placeName><placeName>阿育王寺</placeName></placeName>遇<persName key="A010005">希覺<lb
ed="T" n="0750c23"/><roleName>律師</roleName></persName>，盛揚<persName key="A001519">南山</persName>律，<persName key="A010003">端</persName>則一聽旋有通明，義門<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g586"/><lb
ed="T" n="0750c24"/>無壅。尋投<placeName key="PL000000013517">金華</placeName><persName key="A010006">雲<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>學《名數》<ptr target="#n1275"/>一支并《法<lb
ed="T" n="0750c25"/>華經》。後受<placeName key="PL000000013012">吳興</placeName>緇伍所請講論焉。<ref type="place" target="#PL000000011308 #PL000000008363">兩<name>浙</name></ref><persName key="A003552"><persName>武<lb
ed="T" n="0750c26"/>肅王</persName><persName>錢<roleName>氏</roleName></persName></persName>召於<placeName key="PL000000011489">王府羅漢寺</placeName>演訓，復令於<lb
ed="T" n="0750c27"/><placeName key="PL000000011485">真身塔寺</placeName>宣導。于時有台教師<persName key="A010008">玄燭</persName>者<ptr target="#n1250"/>，彼<lb
ed="T" n="0750c28"/>宗號為第十祖，<persName key="A010003">端</persName>依附<ref type="person" target="#A010008">之</ref>，果了一心三觀<ptr type="glossary" target="#g393"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0750c29"/>遂撰《金光明經隨文釋》十卷。由是兩宗法要，<pb ed="T" n="0751a" xml:id="T50.2061.0751a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0751a01"/>一徑路通。<persName key="A006772"><persName>忠獻王</persName><persName>錢<roleName>氏</roleName></persName></persName>借賜紫衣，別署大<lb
ed="T" n="0751a02"/>德，號<persName key="A010003">崇法</persName>焉。後誓約不出寺門，慕<persName key="A001204">遠<roleName>公</roleName></persName>之<lb
ed="T" n="0751a03"/>不渡<placeName key="PL000000018788">虎溪</placeName>也<ptr target="#n1340"/>。高尚其事，僅二十餘年，身無<lb
ed="T" n="0751a04"/>長衣，口無豐味，居不施關，坐唯一榻。以<date key="j20721592072159" when-iso="+0961-04-11"><name>建<lb
ed="T" n="0751a05"/>隆</name>二年三月十八日</date>，坐滅于<ref type="place" target="#PL000000012759">本房</ref>，容貌猶<lb
ed="T" n="0751a06"/>生。<date key="j20721612072161" when-iso="+0961-04-13">三日</date>，焚之于城西，得舍利於煨燼之末。<lb
ed="T" n="0751a07"/>俗年七十二，僧臘五十二。凡著述傳錄記讚<lb
ed="T" n="0751a08"/>七十許卷，學得其門者止八十餘人。<persName key="A010003">端</persName>性耿<lb
ed="T" n="0751a09"/>介，言無苟且。一坐之間不談世論，唯以佛<lb
ed="T" n="0751a10"/>法為己務，可謂傅翼之象王<ptr target="#n1276"/>矣。祕書監<persName key="A010009">錢<lb
ed="T" n="0751a11"/>昱</persName>甞典<placeName key="PL000000012746">秀郡</placeName>，躬覩<persName key="A010003">端</persName>之標格<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1279"/>，為著《行錄》焉。</p>
